snippet.title: Gaia Attack 4 arcade 2 player 60fps
snippet.description: Best viewed in 60 fps. I'm player 1 and Mark is player 2. The intro is at the end of the video. 34:01 Note that player 1 has a very small cursor in every stage while player 2 doesn't.
